    "The number of instructions in a single batch is initialized to 20.",
    "We use 50 initial templates to form the adversarial set.",
    "We didn't apply perplexity constraints in the JUMP* experiments.",
    "Instead, we added constraints in the experiments with the extended method, which refers to JUMP and JUMP*.",
    "Most of the settings are the same as in JUMP*."
